					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-hypocritic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2070369); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2070369&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164619" alt="The Hypocritic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2070369)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-hypocritic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2070369); return false;" >The Hypocritic</a></span> <span class="odate time_1431809786 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">16 May 2015 20:56</span>
